<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>문제 결과 - 맞추기 사이트</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #4a3b8c;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
        }

        .result-container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 90%;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .result-icon {
            font-size: 80px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .result-message {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .next-button {
            background-color: #4a3b8c;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        .next-button:hover {
            background-color: #3a2b7c;
            color: white;
        }

        .home-button {
            background-color: #6c757d;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .home-button:hover {
            background-color: #5a6268;
            color: white;
        }

        .progress-text {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="result-container">
        <div class="result-icon">
            <% if (isCorrect) { %>
                ⭕
            <% } else { %>
                ❌
            <% } %>
        </div>
        
        <div class="result-message">
            <% if (isCorrect) { %>
                정답입니다!
            <% } else { %>
                아쉽네요!
            <% } %>
        </div>

        <div class="progress-text">
            <%= currentQuizId %> / <%= totalQuizzes %> 문제
        </div>

        <div>
            <a href="/quiz/play/<%= nextQuizId %>" class="next-button">다음 문제</a>
            <a href="/" class="home-button">홈으로</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 